0:34:19.34,000 --> 0:34:21,000
(Rires)

661
0:34:23.42,000 --> 0:34:24,000
CA : OK.

662
0:34:24.635,000 --> 0:34:26,000
EM : Bien que le lanceur ait l'air plutôt grand,

